# Agent Reflection — FR-04 Fix (Threshold Evaluation Bug)

## Reasoning Log
No reasoning.log found in worktree. Proceeding based on review feedback only.

## Constraints Applied
- [FR-04 Spec] Alert thresholds: leaf [14,7,3,1], chain [30,14,7]. A cert with 2 days remaining must trigger the 3-day threshold, not 14-day.
- [Conventions] Only modify alert_service_impl.py — do not touch shared files.

## Review Feedback
- Threshold evaluation iterated [14,7,3,1] ascending with `days_remaining <= threshold` + break, causing 2-day cert to match 14-day threshold. Fixed by sorting thresholds ascending ([1,3,7,14]) so smallest applicable threshold matches first.

